üë• USER RESEARCH INSIGHTS
Primary Pain Points (from Reddit, Quora, Forums)

Brittle, breaking nails - #1 complaint, especially after gel/acrylic removal
Peeling/splitting nail layers - caused by water exposure, harsh chemicals
Slow nail growth - frustration with time it takes to grow damaged nails out
Yellow nail staining - from dark polish, smoking, nail products
Damaged cuticles - hangnails, dryness, cracking, infection concerns
Nail biting habit - difficulty stopping, looking for deterrents
Weak nails after salon services - gel, acrylic, dip powder damage
Ridges and texture issues - vertical lines, rough surface, bumps
Dry, flaky nails - lack of moisture, excessive hand washing/sanitizing
Not knowing proper nail care basics - confusion about cutting vs pushing cuticles, filing direction, etc.

